  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform GPU acceleration via blade-graphics (Vulkan + Metal)",
    "E-graph (egglog) based kernel fusion and optimization",
    "Automatic differentiation for full training support",
    "Zero-compile-time model execution (no JIT warmup)",
    "HuggingFace safetensors weight loading",
    "KV-cache for efficient autoregressive inference",
    "Built-in transformer primitives (GQA, RoPE, RMSNorm, SwiGLU)",
    "Perfetto trace profiling support"
  ],
